    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone seeking a dependable daily driver. While the mechanical components have been well-maintained, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the hood, and a few minor dings. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows typical wear and tear from regular use. It's a solid, honest car that isn't perfect to look at but will get you where you need to go without issue.",
